{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We used to go there, actually, now that I think about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember having one Purim there, and they had a play, you know, on the stage where the older-- older orphanage people, the members, performed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and Passover-- and I remember now, come to think of it, that's where we used to go because I don't-- I didn't remember anything in the house, really, but I do remember going to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's-- that's where we all-- everybody went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everybody went there later on, you know, because that was like the central place, you know, for everybody to get together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was a fairly sizable place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There probably were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- I remember something, but I don't really remember, you know, because it went sort of by me, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was adults talking to each other, and-- and they sort of try to shield you from that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't really know-- I know that some of the older-- older boys-- the orphanage was to about, I think, age 16 or 17 or 18.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they had problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were beaten up sometimes, you know, if they caught them on their own.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to go with a few of them together, always.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was always the-- you had to make sure that nobody gets caught on his own.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But really, actual incident, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Till-- till the Kristallnacht, of course, which we'll mention in-- want me to mention the Kristallnacht?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, we'll get to that shortly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How-- how did your family-- or did they try to explain to you what was going on?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know because, really-- the-- I'll tell you who tried to explain to me, strangely enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
